    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What is Environmental Engineering?</h2>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>Environmental Engineering is a discipline that applies scientific and engineering principles to protect human health and the environment. It focuses on developing solutions for critical challenges such as clean water access, air pollution control, waste management, and ecosystem restoration while promoting sustainable development.</p>
                    <p>As an environmental engineer, you'll design systems and processes that minimize pollution, conserve resources, and remediate contaminated sites. You'll work at the intersection of multiple disciplines, including civil engineering, chemistry, biology, and public health, to address complex environmental problems. This field requires both technical expertise and an understanding of environmental regulations and policies.</p>
                    <p>With growing concerns about climate change, resource depletion, and environmental degradation, environmental engineers play a crucial role in creating a sustainable future. The field continues to evolve with innovations in renewable energy, green infrastructure, and circular economy approaches, making this an impactful and dynamic career path.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Areas Section -->
    <section class="section bg-dark" id="key-areas">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Key Areas of Study</h2>
            <p class="section-intro">Environmental Engineering encompasses critical disciplines for protecting our environment and public health:</p>
            
            <div class="cards-grid three-columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-tint"></i> Water Resources Engineering</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Management and protection of water resources for sustainable use.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Hydrology</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Water cycle, watershed management</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Hydraulic Systems</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Flow control, distribution networks</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Flood Control</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Mitigation strategies, modeling</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-filter"></i> Water & Wastewater Treatment</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Design of systems to purify water and treat wastewater for safe disposal or reuse.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Treatment Processes</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Physical, chemical, biological</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Water Quality</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Testing, standards, monitoring</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Resource Recovery</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Energy, nutrients, water reuse</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-wind"></i> Air Quality Management</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Control and prevention of air pollution from various sources.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Pollution Control</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Emissions reduction, scrubbers</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Air Dispersion</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Modeling, impact assessment</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Indoor Air Quality</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Ventilation, contaminant control</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-grid three-columns" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i> Solid & Hazardous Waste</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Management and treatment of waste materials to minimize environmental impact.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Waste Minimization</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Source reduction, recycling</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Treatment Technologies</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Incineration, stabilization</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Landfill Design</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Containment, gas collection</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-seedling"></i> Environmental Remediation</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Cleanup and restoration of contaminated sites and ecosystems.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Site Assessment</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Sampling, risk evaluation</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Soil Remediation</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Bioremediation, thermal treatment</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Groundwater Cleanup</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Pump and treat, permeable barriers</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-solar-panel"></i> Sustainable Systems</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Design of environmentally friendly infrastructure and processes.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Green Infrastructure</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Bioswales, permeable pavements</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Renewable Energy</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Solar, wind, biomass systems</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Life Cycle Assessment</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Environmental impact evaluation</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

